Ing '''Kaiping''' ([[Chinese Postal Map Romanisation]]: '''Hoiping'''; {{zh|t=開平 |s=开平 |p=Kāipíng|y= Hoi1 Ping4}}; Kaiping dialect ([[Yale_Romanization#Cantonese|Yale Romanization]]): Hoi3 Pen6) metung yang [[lakanbalen a kadaneng kondadu]] (''county-level city'') king lalawigan ning [[Guangdong]], [[Maldang Republika ning Tsina]]. Atyu king Pearl River Delta at kayabe ya king and is part of the [[Labuad ning Keragulang Taishan]] (''Greater Taishan Region''), ing penibatan da reng pipumpunan da reng dakal a [[Overseas Chinese]]. Maki populasyun yang  680,000 anyang 2003 at maki lapad yang {{convert|1,659|km²}}.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.xzqh.org/html/gd/07_55.html|title=Profile of Kaiping|publisher=|date=|accessdate=2008-07-12|language=Chinese}} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref> Metung yang uri ning  [[Taishan dialect]] ing salita da reng tau keni.

